<br>
Essentially it's the raw xp value of the mob divided using their formula across multiple people with a penalty assessed.  Not ideal for normal xp situations, but welcomed for raid situations.<br>
<br>
It will always be better to raid mobs killable by 1 grp with 1 grp, than to raid on them.  But it does make multi grp xp raids viable for ToV, I guess.. doubt it's more efficient than single grp.. but may be more fun. <p>Nicolai, Haste Puller<br>
